### 5.2 PART B Questions (14 Marks Each — Module Internal Choice)

---

#### **Question A (14 Marks)** `[KTU University Exam - Dec 2024]`

**(a)** Design an HTML registration form with the following fields: **Name, Email, Age, Phone Number, Password, Confirm Password, and Gender (radio buttons)**. Apply appropriate styling using CSS. **(7 marks)**

**(b)** Write a JavaScript function `validateRegistrationForm()` that performs the following validations on the form designed in part (a):
- Name must not be empty and must contain only alphabets.
- Email must match a valid email pattern.
- Age must be a number between 18 and 60.
- Phone must be exactly 10 digits.
- Password and Confirm Password must match and be at least 8 characters long.
- A gender must be selected.
- Display error messages beside each field and prevent submission if any validation fails. **(7 marks)**

---

